<br />
How about a Troubadour's Mace? It goes for 7-15k depending on your server. 
<br />
There's always Battle-Drummer's Main Gauche, but I find that goes for over 10k generally.
<br />
Are you looking for stats or are you looking for raw damage? There's the Scimitar of Emerald Dawn which at 20/34 makes a good offhand weapon. It goes for around 5k if you can find one.
<br />

